name: Experiment Or Die #19
description: A yearlong project to create a new collage every day using my years of photos and personal assets. I've been obsessed with skate culture since I was a kid, though I never really got any good at it. As an adult these worn out relics of the 80's remind me of what it was to be a kid, screwing off all summer, getting in trouble and doing something death defying. IG: Nikejerk
